<div class="about-hero">
  <div class="about-hero__inner page-width">
    <p class="about-hero__eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
    <h1 class="about-hero__title">Joy in Every Touch</h1>
    <p class="about-hero__lead">
      JOY is a Seoul-based B2B platform connecting licensed medical professionals and aesthetic clinics worldwide with premium Korean aesthetic products, top-tier beauty talent, and hands-on clinical education.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="about-pillars page-width">
  <div class="about-pillars__grid">

    <div class="about-pillar">
      <div class="about-pillar__number">01</div>
      <div class="about-pillar__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M24 4C13 4 4 13 4 24s9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20S35 4 24 4z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M16 24h16M24 16v16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="about-pillar__title">Medical Aesthetics<br>Distribution</h2>
      <p class="about-pillar__body">
        We source and supply Korea's most trusted injectable and topical aesthetic products — including Nabota, Botulax, Yvoire, Rejuran, and more — exclusively to verified clinics and licensed medical professionals. Every product in our catalog is clinically validated and sourced directly from Korean manufacturers, ensuring authenticity, cold-chain integrity, and competitive wholesale pricing.
      </p>
      <ul class="about-pillar__list">
        <li>Botulinum toxins &amp; HA fillers</li>
        <li>Skin boosters &amp; regenerative care</li>
        <li>Direct manufacturer sourcing</li>
        <li>B2B wholesale pricing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-pillar">
      <div class="about-pillar__number">02</div>
      <div class="about-pillar__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="24" cy="16" r="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="M8 40c0-8.837 7.163-16 16-16s16 7.163 16 16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="about-pillar__title">Beauty Professional<br>Placement</h2>
      <p class="about-pillar__body">
        Korea is home to some of the world's most skilled aesthetic and beauty professionals. JOY bridges the gap between exceptional Korean talent — aestheticians, skincare specialists, and clinical beauty therapists — and clinics, spas, and wellness centers seeking to elevate their service offering with authentic K-beauty expertise.
      </p>
      <ul class="about-pillar__list">
        <li>Certified Korean aestheticians</li>
        <li>Clinical beauty therapists</li>
        <li>Short-term &amp; long-term placements</li>
        <li>Multilingual talent network</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-pillar">
      <div class="about-pillar__number">03</div>
      <div class="about-pillar__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect x="6" y="10" width="36" height="28" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="M6 18h36" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="M16 28l4 4 8-8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="about-pillar__title">Clinical Treatment<br>Seminars</h2>
      <p class="about-pillar__body">
        Staying at the forefront of aesthetic medicine requires continuous education. JOY organizes hands-on training seminars and clinical workshops led by leading Korean dermatologists and aesthetic physicians. From injection techniques to advanced skin protocols, our programs are designed for practicing professionals who demand the very best.
      </p>
      <ul class="about-pillar__list">
        <li>Hands-on injection workshops</li>
        <li>Korean dermatology protocols</li>
        <li>Certified continuing education</li>
        <li>Small-group &amp; private sessions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="about-mission">
  <div class="about-mission__inner page-width">
    <div class="about-mission__quote">
      <span class="about-mission__quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
      <p>We believe that great aesthetics starts with the right products, the right people, and the right knowledge. JOY exists to make all three accessible — wherever you practice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="about-values page-width">
  <h2 class="about-values__heading">Why Clinics Choose JOY</h2>
  <div class="about-values__grid">
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="about-value__title">Verified Sources Only</h3>
        <p class="about-value__body">Every product is sourced directly from licensed Korean manufacturers with full documentation and cold-chain compliance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="about-value__title">Medical Professionals First</h3>
        <p class="about-value__body">Our catalog is exclusively available to licensed clinics and practitioners. No retail. No grey market.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="about-value__title">Dedicated Account Support</h3>
        <p class="about-value__body">Every B2B account gets a dedicated point of contact for orders, compliance questions, and product guidance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value__icon" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>
      <div>
        <h3 class="about-value__title">Education-Backed</h3>
        <p class="about-value__body">We don't just supply — we train. Our seminar network keeps your team current with the latest Korean aesthetic innovations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="about-cta">
  <div class="about-cta__inner page-width">
    <h2 class="about-cta__title">Ready to work with JOY?</h2>
    <p class="about-cta__body">Whether you're sourcing products, looking for talent, or booking a seminar — we'd love to hear from you.</p>
    <div class="about-cta__actions">
      <a href="/pages/inquiry" class="button about-cta__btn about-cta__btn--primary">Submit a B2B Inquiry</a>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="button about-cta__btn about-cta__btn--secondary">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .about-hero {
    background-color: #1a4a38;
    color: #f7ede5;
    padding-block: 80px 72px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .about-hero__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c49a5e;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .about-hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    color: #f7ede5;
  }

  .about-hero__lead {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(247, 237, 229, 0.82);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  /* ── Pillars ── */
  .about-pillars {
    padding-block: 80px;
  }

  .about-pillars__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px 48px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 989px) {
    .about-pillars__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 56px;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }

  .about-pillar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .about-pillar__number {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #c49a5e;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .about-pillar__icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    color: #1a4a38;
    margin-top: -6px;
  }

  .about-pillar__icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .about-pillar__title {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a4a38;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .about-pillar__body {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .about-pillar__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 4px 0 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .about-pillar__list li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #1a4a38;
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-pillar__list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #c49a5e;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ── Mission quote ── */
  .about-mission {
    background-color: #f7ede5;
    padding-block: 64px;
  }

  .about-mission__inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-mission__quote {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-mission__quote-mark {
    display: block;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 6rem;
    line-height: 0.6;
    color: #c49a5e;
    opacity: 0.35;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .about-mission__quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.2vw, 1.375rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1a4a38;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Values ── */
  .about-values {
    padding-block: 72px;
  }

  .about-values__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    color: #1a4a38;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .about-values__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px 48px;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 749px) {
    .about-values__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }
  }

  .about-value {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-value__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background-color: #1a4a38;
    color: #f7ede5;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .about-value__title {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a4a38;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .about-value__body {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .about-cta {
    background-color: #1a4a38;
    padding-block: 72px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-cta__inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .about-cta__title {
    font-family: var(--font-primary--family);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);
    color: #f7ede5;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .about-cta__body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(247, 237, 229, 0.75);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .about-cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .about-cta__btn {
    padding: 13px 30px;
    border-radius: var(--button-border-radius, 4px);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .about-cta__btn--primary {
    background-color: #c49a5e;
    color: #fff;
    border: 1.5px solid #c49a5e;
  }

  .about-cta__btn--primary:hover {
    background-color: #a87d45;
    border-color: #a87d45;
  }

  .about-cta__btn--secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: #f7ede5;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(247, 237, 229, 0.5);
  }

  .about-cta__btn--secondary:hover {
    border-color: #f7ede5;
    background-color: rgba(247, 237, 229, 0.08);
  }

  @media (max-width: 749px) {
    .about-hero {
      padding-block: 56px 48px;
    }

    .about-pillars {
      padding-block: 56px;
    }

    .about-mission {
      padding-block: 48px;
    }

    .about-values {
      padding-block: 52px;
    }

    .about-cta {
      padding-block: 52px;
    }

    .about-cta__actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-cta__btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

